These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice
There 2 different types of food: papaya, pumpkin
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, gardening
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, martial-arts
1. the person watching animation movies is not to the right of the person eating pumpkin##8
2. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
3. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | juice     | sprite      |
| Food          | pumpkin | papaya    |
| Hobby         | gardening   | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | martial-arts      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, skydiving
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, lawyer
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, roller
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
3. the lawyer is not to the right of the manager##8
4. the person driving the car is not the person who's hobby is skydiving##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | coffee        | hot-chocolate    |
| Hobby       | puzzles         | skydiving |
| Job         | lawyer | manager   |
| Transport   | car               | roller  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, disaster
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, electronic
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, indian
2 different pets are kept: horse, bird
1. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
2. the indian is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
3. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery       | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | country       | electronic    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | indian |
| Pet           | horse        | bird   |

 #################################

 
